---
title: Chermoula Beef & Crouton Salad with Roasted Pumpkin, Almonds & Garlic Aioli
description: Who doesn’t like a bit of char on their beef? This one gets a generous coating of our punchy chermoula spice blend before it crisps up in the pan until golden. Finish it off with a bowl of roasted veggies and crunchy croutons for an outstanding pairing of flavours.

